<item>
            <title>[FLINK-1499] Make TaskManager to disconnect from JobManager in case of a restart</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1499</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In case of a TaskManager restart, the TaskManager does not unregisters from the JobManager. However, it tries to reconnect once the restart has been finished. In order to maintain a consistent state, the TaskManager should disconnect from the JobManager upon restart or termination.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
